        <div class="tl-item"><div class="tl-line"><div class="tl-dot"></div></div><div class="tl-card"><div class="tl-phase">Phase 7</div><div class="tl-title">🔐 Credentials Generated ✅</div><div class="tl-desc">A random secure password is auto-generated and stored in Kubernetes. Retrieve anytime via <code style="color:var(--cyan)">abctl local credentials</code>. Airbyte is now live!</div></div></div>
      </div>

